1
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:27,960
Young Master.

2
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,160
I have checked.

3
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:31,600
That Fang Zhuozhuo is indeed Fang Qingcheng's cousin,

4
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:34,530
and also indeed a flower servant at Yanzhi Pavilion.

5
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:36,040
But I didn't find out

6
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:38,300
that any elder in her family passed away.

7
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:40,080
To be exact,

8
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:43,160
I can't find anything about her family background at all.

9
00:00:43,160 --> 00:00:44,960
Since she has no feelings for me,

10
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:46,120
then

11
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:50,160
why did she marry into the mansion in Qingcheng's place?

12
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:50,800
Could it

13
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:53,680
really be because of their deep sisterly bond?

14
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:56,520
Fang Qingcheng's whereabouts are currently unknown.

15
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:59,050
The most important thing is to find her first.

16
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,800
We cannot affect the grand plan.

17
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,280
Later,

18
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,519
go find a few capable guards

19
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:08,720
and set off to the back mountain immediately to look for her.

20
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:09,920
Put on plain clothes.

21
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:12,960
Follow me to Yanzhi Pavilion early tomorrow morning,

22
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:16,360
and bring Fang Zhuozhuo.

23
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:28,840
You are the closest person to Qingcheng.

24
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,280
I

25
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:34,100
am just doing some trivial things for the Pavilion Master.

26
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:38,520
I heard you were the dowry maid of Qingcheng's grandmother.

27
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:40,640
Qingcheng's family passed away early,

28
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:42,000
and you have been taking care of her.

29
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,400
You seem like master and servant,

30
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,920
but you are more like family.

31
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,759
With such a close relationship,

32
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,759
how could you not know Qingcheng's whereabouts?

33
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:51,360
My Lord, please understand.

34
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:54,479
The Pavilion Master is dedicated to developing cosmetics.

35
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:56,080
To pick rare flowers and herbs,

36
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,210
she travels around.

37
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:59,880
It's common for her not to return for over ten days.

38
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:02,280
Before leaving to pick flowers this time, the Pavilion Master said

39
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:04,240
she would definitely be back before the wedding.

40
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,080
So,

41
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,920
I didn't take it to heart.

42
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,600
Yes.

43
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:12,000
My cousin went to the back mountain to pick Jinlumei.

44
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,560
That flower grows in the crevices of cliffs

45
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,680
and is extremely difficult to pick.

46
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,840
Perhaps there were none on the back mountain,

47
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,770
so she might have

48
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:20,160
gone somewhere else.

49
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:21,440
Yes.

50
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:24,980
The Pavilion Master did say she was going to pick Jinlumei.

51
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,680
Qingcheng left at the Si hour.

52
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,880
Why do you remember so clearly?

53
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:31,440
That day, I

54
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:33,480
had an appointment with a customer at the pavilion at the Si hour

55
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:36,740
to study the bridal makeup powder for her wedding banquet.

56
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:39,400
Before leaving, the Pavilion Master specially reminded me

57
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,000
that the customer likes rose dew,

58
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,260
and told me to add more.

59
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,160
Good thing I prepared in advance.

60
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:47,440
The Pavilion Master worked hard for the Makeup Selection Ceremony,

61
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:49,720
saying she must surpass the Linlang Pavilion in the East Market

62
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:51,560
and make Yanzhi Pavilion win first place.

63
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:54,200
It seems the Pavilion Master attaches great importance to the Makeup Selection Ceremony.

64
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:56,240
Madam Li is holding this Makeup Selection Ceremony,

65
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:58,200
so everyone is secretly saying

66
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:01,680
that the Pavilion Master agreed to marry just for this ceremony.

67
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,040
My Lord, please understand.

68
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:05,570
I saw with my own eyes that when my cousin left,

69
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:08,000
she kept your birth date paper close to her body.

70
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,000
She is deeply in love with you.

71
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:16,079
Before your Pavilion Master went missing,

72
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,480
was there anything strange?

73
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,720
There was nothing strange about the Pavilion Master,

74
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:20,579
but as for this flower servant...

75
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,840
Forgive me, Third Young Master.

76
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,200
It just slipped out.

77
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:27,200
However, this Lady Fang is quite strange.

78
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,800
Although she and the Pavilion Master are sisters,

79
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:32,000
none of us have ever seen them together.

80
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,960
They are obviously not close.

81
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,400
She risked her life to take the Pavilion Master's place.

82
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:38,000
She must have her own agenda.

83
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,480
Yes.

84
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:42,240
There is a world of difference between my cousin and me.

85
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:44,240
She is usually busy with her affairs,

86
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:46,000
so she can't often be with me.

87
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,440
But she brought me to Kuizhou

88
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,040
and gave me a place to stay.

89
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:53,440
I have nothing but love and admiration for her.

90
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:56,680
Marrying in her place was indeed for her sake.

91
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:59,160
But right after she went missing,

92
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,600
someone is trying to sow discord.

93
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:04,240
I think that person has an agenda.

94
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,080
Also,

95
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,680
that day,

96
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,560
I saw with my own eyes

97
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,960
that you and she had an argument in the backyard.

98
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,280
She clearly told you

99
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,680
that the hibiscus paste you made had an uneven color

100
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,210
and asked you to improve it.

101
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,880
You were very dissatisfied.

102
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:22,520
Could her disappearance be related to you?

103
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,800
What nonsense are you talking about?

104
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,200
I was discussing with the Pavilion Master

105
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,400
the techniques of making cosmetics.

106
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:28,530
What does a flower slave like you know?

107
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,840
My Lord, it's better to be safe

108
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:32,920
than sorry.

109
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,920
If someone around her harbors evil intentions,

110
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:38,120
you must interrogate them carefully.

111
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,480
Don't let the culprit go.

112
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,040
You...

113
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:46,580
Young Master, someone has seen Fang Qingcheng.

114
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:47,930
Let's go.

115
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,260
Send a few men to keep an eye on this place.

116
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:00,880
Yes, sir.

117
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,840
Chu Shengyi is investigating so closely.

118
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:08,400
I must get the Qionghua flower at this birthday banquet

119
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,530
and escape quickly.

120
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,640
If you want to plant these flowers

121
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,900
in the Master's manor,

122
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:16,360
you will violate the Third Master's taboo.

123
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,600
What taboo?

124
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,770
It's just a show for others.

125
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:24,050
Saying that flowers will ruin the manor's feng shui.

126
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,480
I think

127
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:28,520
he is just begging Madam Li for mercy like a dog.

128
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,580
Madam Li treats him like this,

129
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,560
yet he

130
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:34,320
even avoids mentioning his birth mother's background.

131
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:36,360
Such a shameless person

132
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,360
is truly despicable.

133
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:40,800
Such a person is the most terrifying.

134
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,600
As the saying goes, better to provoke a gentleman's anger

135
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,260
than a villain's resentment.

136
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,120
If you really piss him off...

137
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,920
I want to piss him off.

138
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,880
The more he bans flowers,

139
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,580
the more I will plant them.

140
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,200
Making him lose all face

141
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,480
will naturally please Madam Li.

142
00:05:57,159 --> 00:06:00,020
That's my shortcut to attend the birthday banquet.

143
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:01,840
Besides Madam Li,

144
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:04,460
isn't there also the Grand Governor?

145
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,760
Everyone knows

146
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,720
that our Grand Governor is of royal descent

147
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,240
and values face the most.

148
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,640
Chu Shengyi's birth mother, Concubine Zhao,

149
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,800
was originally a flower slave.

150
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,800
This is a taboo in the Governor's manor.

151
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,560
If you make such a big scene

152
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,680
and really anger the Governor,

153
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,240
wouldn't it be

154
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:26,720
dangerous?

155
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,240
Don't worry.

156
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,800
Just tell me what you saw.

157
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,159
I won't make things difficult for you.

158
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:36,760
I was chopping wood in the back mountain that day,

159
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:41,400
and I saw a plump girl walking into the mountain.

160
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,120
Is it her?

161
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,560
The person in this portrait?

162
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:58,080
Then, about an hour later,

163
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:00,760
when I finished chopping wood and was about to go home,

164
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:03,520
I saw another skinny girl walking out of the mountain.

165
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:05,760
It's easy to get lost in the back mountain if you are not careful.

166
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,560
Few people usually go there.

167
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:10,080
Seeing two girls in one day,

168
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,160
I thought it was strange too.

169
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,600
Does the skinny girl you saw look like this?

170
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,640
Yes, that's her.

171
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,040
You may go back first.

172
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,640
We interrogated her for so long yesterday,

173
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:31,000
but Lady Fang never mentioned she had been to the back mountain.

174
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,880
Fang Zhuozhuo and Fang Qingcheng

175
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:35,720
appearing at the same place at the same time

176
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,000
is just too much of a coincidence.

177
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:40,130
So it is highly possible that these two

178
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,120
are plotting something.

